Class AheadBuildErrorEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.ahead.wrapper.AheadBuildErrorEvent

  • public class AheadBuildErrorEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    The AheadBuildErrorEvent is dispatched when ever a syntax error was found during the compilation step. The Event contains all needed information to set an error marker
    Author:
    Tom Brosch, Thomas Thuem
